---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy | AppCompare — Shopify App Comparison Tool" description="Privacy policy for app-compare.com — how we collect, use, and protect your information.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>

    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>AppCompare ("we", "our") operates app-compare.com — an independent resource for comparing Shopify apps. We are not affiliated with Shopify Inc. Contact: <a href="mailto:privacy@app-compare.com">privacy@app-compare.com</a></p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p><strong>Analytics data:</strong> We use Google Analytics 4 to collect anonymized usage data including pages visited, session duration, and general geographic location. This data does not identify you personally.</p>
    <p><strong>Cookies:</strong> Google Analytics sets cookies. Opt out via the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics opt-out add-on</a>.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To understand how visitors use our site and improve our comparisons</li>
      <li>We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>AppCompare participates in affiliate programs. When you click a link to a Shopify app and install it, we may receive a referral commission. This does not affect our independent ratings or reviews.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights (GDPR / CCPA)</h2>
    <p>If you are in the EU, UK, or California, you have the right to access, correct, or delete any personal data we hold. Email <a href="mailto:privacy@app-compare.com">privacy@app-compare.com</a> to exercise these rights.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Analytics data is retained for 14 months per Google Analytics default settings.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>Material changes will be noted with an updated date above.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
